{
  "texts": [
    "The data at node m of the tree is denoted by Q m.",
    "The k denotes the index of the labels of the samples and P mk denotes the prediction probability at node m.",
    "In order to predict the belt abrasive wear which affects the surface polishing quality of machining workpieces, two types of sensors, i.e.",
    "three-axis accelerometer and threeaxis dynamometer are utilized in this research.",
    "The research methodology including the experiment preparation and the data acquisition process is detailed in the following subsections."
  ]
}